572
00:24:47,260 --> 00:24:49,080
 zatomljeno jecanje

573
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:51,640
 preselio sam se pod krov

574
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,620
 na sijeno

575
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:54,780
 namjestio sam ležaj

576
00:24:54,780 --> 00:24:55,700
 u sijenu

577
00:24:55,700 --> 00:24:57,360
 a stol sam postavio

578
00:24:57,360 --> 00:24:58,120
 kraj vrata

579
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,800
 mrzovoljan

580
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:00,880
 potišten

581
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,560
 i u crnim brigama

582
